    "summary": "The user asks for a breakdown of arguments regarding nuclear energy, and the assistant immediately responds with a prescriptive endorsement of nuclear power. As the conversation progresses, the user attempts to introduce counterarguments regarding cost and renewables, but the assistant consistently dismisses these concerns, characterizing them as inferior or short-sighted in favor of a pro-nuclear stance.",
